metadata.name: Poseidon
metadata.description:
It is very rare to decide on the name of the photograph while taking it. 
He is just one of the people who collects garbage that is accumulated from the sea - with the current on the shore of the estuary(Golden Horn) all day before the snow storm. And by doing this virtuous task, he is the God of the Sea for me.

Photographer: Melih Taner Tanyeli  
Edition: Open  
Location: Istanbul - Turkey  
Jpeg Size: 5680x3787/300dpi
